                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <add>ק\"ק שארית ישראל</add>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">Congregation Shearith Israel,</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>9th Shebat 5628</date></p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>2d Feby 1868</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>At a meeting of the Board of Trustees held this day the following<lb/> resolutions\n                were unanimously adopted:</p>\n            <p><hi rend=\"underline\">Resolved</hi> — that the Trustees of the Congregation <add>שארית\n                    ישראל</add><lb/> learn with sincere regret of the death of the <persName>Reverend<lb/>\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">Isaac Leeser</hi></persName> the much respected\n                    <add>חזן</add> of the Congn<lb/>\n                <add>בית אל אמת</add> of <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> — distinguished alike\n                for<lb/> his many virtues, his fearless devotion to the House of<lb/>\n                <placeName>Israel</placeName> during a long period of usefulness, and with an<lb/>\n                ability which marked him as the earnest champion of<lb/> orthodox Judaism.</p>\n            <p><hi rend=\"underline\">Resolved</hi> — that we tender the Congregation <add>בית אל\n                    אמת</add> our warmest<lb/> sympathies for their severe bereavement, and offer\n                the<lb/> assurance of our respect and condolence on the melancholy<lb/> occasion.<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Resolved </hi>— that the <add>חזן</add> of this Congn, the\n                    <persName>Revd I. I. Lyons</persName>, be requested<lb/> to make an Escoba in\n                our Holy place of worship on<lb/> then ensuing <add>שבת</add> for the Reverend\n                deceased, and also on<lb/> the expiration of the <add>שלשים</add>.</p>\n            <p><hi rend=\"underline\">Resolved</hi> — that, as a further mark to respect for the\n                deceased, and<lb/> for the congregation he so faithfully and creditably served,</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rv0ds35/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
