                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>a committee from this Board with the <add>חזן</add> of the<lb/> Congregation be\n                requested to attend the <add>לויה</add> at <placeName>Philada</placeName><lb/> and\n                to present to the President of the Congregation <add>בית אל אמת</add><lb/> a copy of\n                these Resolutions”</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">Extract from the minutes</hi>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Mark<add>?</add> Phillips</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Clerk</p>"
